{"about_the_game":"<strong>Delve into an intricate story about a grieving father, who finds himself involved in paranormal events related to a secretive cult and a mysterious girl.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/gif1.gif?t=1726572936\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Repent</h2>Explore the story of Robert Watford, a retired cop with a heavy alcohol addiction and troubled past, as he starts his new job as a night shift guard of the Colony Tower. Rob will find himself in the middle of paranormal events involving a strange girl and a mysterious cult, leaving him no choice but to take matters into his own hands to try to understand what's happening and why. Rob will face various instances in which his decisions directly affect the outcome of the story and the people involved.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/gif2.gif?t=1726572936\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Repent is primarily a first-person narrative walking simulator that focuses on exploration. The player will be able to complete tasks and interact with the tenants of the Colony Tower through conversations or secondary events, to learn more about the location, its people and the many mysteries that lie within the building. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/extras/gif3.gif?t=1726572936\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Conversation system with various dialog options.<br></li><li> Deep story with multiple endings.<br></li><li> Immersion focused horror.<br></li><li> Randomly generated secondary events, making each playthrough unique.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Daily tasks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/bc97d452fac23a818b261f9245d54ea4a80ac206.jpg"},{"name":"Love cures all","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/5e73a87a0d6a6c1540c8b2e375a61aa9ac55ecb9.jpg"},{"name":"Second chances","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/d351ff95a5516c4976358a020d6127f0e3a63115.jpg"},{"name":"Regret","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/385b137a8707e2f71190e1673e5a0e4e7a7822de.jpg"},{"name":"Life moves on","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/247108771ec2bbb1a4bded7c7d8fd2b2dd0dd4ef.jpg"},{"name":"Repent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/0eb7ce9203d8133a93a3f2325400a3dc338e9434.jpg"},{"name":"Trust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2607050/c61aa50b4c32c047b236c591c4b062abbd93b89c.jpg"}],"total":7},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726572936","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1726572936","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726572936","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607050/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726572936","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"There are mentions and conversations about self harm and depression.\r\nThere are mentions about loss of a loved one.\r\nThere are mentions of abuse of alcohol substances."},"detailed_description":"<strong>Delve into an intricate story about a grieving father, who finds himself involved in paranormal events related to a secretive cult and a mysterious girl.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_i